            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <p class="review__text">"Great customer service and fantastic products."</p>
            <div class="review__author">
                <img src="./images/customer2.jpg" alt="Customer 2" class="review__img">
                <h4 class="review__name">Jane Smith</h4>
